  "title": "docs: add a guide to explain how to conditionally display content",
  "body": "About #1266\n\nNoResults/EmptyQuery were'nt enough to achieve simple use case like NoResults/HasResults (like in the e-commerce example). You need to quickly go to a custom widgets. So this is a guide to explain how to do it for now.\n\nMay be replace by a better solution when our state management will be easier. \n",
